metadata.name: Nature, Human, Pain
metadata.description:
180 cm x 160 cm (acrylic and oil paint mix)
(if you want to buy physical painting pls contact me on twitter before you buy)

Exclusion of nature, In fact, if we bring a different perspective to humanism, we can say that this concept, which is based on human, brings about the exclusion of thoughts other than human. As a result, in this painting, while depicting human and nature in one body, It also tells about the struggle for existence in the same body.
